<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.2">
<l>nāḷaiva tuvaima ṇameṉṟu nāḷiṭṭup</l>
<l>pāḷai kamuku paricuṭaip pantaṟkīḻ</l>
<l>kōḷari mātavaṉ kōvinta ṉeṉpāṉōr</l>
<l>kāḷaipu kutakka ṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that the unique young Man</l>
<l>called the mightly Lion, Mādhava, Govinda</l>
<l>entered under the superior pandal made of areca palms with spathes,</l>
<l>with the morrow being fixed as the wedding date.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
